import { Route, Switch } from "react-router-dom"
import Home from '../pages/Home'
import Signup from "../pages/Signup"

const Routes = () => {
    return(
        <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/">
                <Home />
            </Route>

            <Route exact path="/signup">
                <Signup />
            </Route>
        </Switch>
    )
}

export default Routes
